object.script:
INIT = 0 RUNNING = 1 STOPPED = 2
state = INIT ticks = 0 values = {}
function onTick() if state == RUNNING then ticks = ticks + 1 end
local start = input.getBool(1) local stop = input.getBool(2) local value = input.getNumber(1)
if start and state == INIT then ticks = 0 state = RUNNING elseif stop and state == RUNNING then state = STOPPED end if state == RUNNING then table.insert(values, value) end
output.setNumber(1, ticks / 60.0) end
function onDraw() local w,h = screen.getWidth(), screen.getHeight() local maxV = 900 screen.setColor(255,255,0)
for i,v in pairs(values) do local x = (i-1)/ticks * w local y = (1-(v/maxV)) * h screen.drawRectF(x, y, 1, 1) end end
